{"tid":2286279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港破千萬票房｜《鬼滅》韓上映前急改炭治郎旭日旗耳環 粉絲被鬧賣國賊","createTime":"2020-11-15T00:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T15:03:34.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8089b1c2386b44725c325ff7538dd7c32ed54bfc","tid":2286279,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"《鬼滅》主角炭治郎的耳環設計與旭日旗相似，在韓國版電影已更改設計。<br />\n<br />\n日本人氣動畫電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》於前日在香港開畫，上畫第三日票房已衝破1,000萬。在武漢肺炎疫情下，成績依然相當突出。電影暫定於12月10日在韓國上畫，但當地的《鬼滅》粉絲卻被指為賣國賊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2_Gebp4SP11mu3cEf2CI5jgIC9I=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BEWYGFXMM5CVHEJFGCQN5K2U3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2_Gebp4SP11mu3cEf2CI5jgIC9I%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBEWYGFXMM5CVHEJFGCQN5K2U3M.jpg&h=9b701e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日有韓國《鬼滅》粉絲在當地著名Q&amp;A網站「NAVER知識iN」留言表示困擾：「雖然我很喜歡鬼滅，但卻被周圍的人問我是不是賣國賊。雖然從歷史問題上思考，就知道這部動畫是有點那個。但之前看了《無限列車篇》的新預告片，總之就是勁！」該粉絲提出問題後，有網民直指他是賣國賊，亦有人叫他不要理會別人的說話。至於為何《鬼滅》會被指為右翼漫畫，原因有三個，第一是因為主角炭治郎的耳環設計與旭日旗相似。旭日旗是舊日本軍使用的旗幟，因此被日本在二次世界大戰期間侵略過的地區，均會視旭日旗為冒犯性的圖案和日本軍國主義的象徵。而第二是因為《鬼滅》的故事發生於大正時代，對韓國來說，是與日本殖民統治時期重疊。至於第三個原因是因為動畫的聲優與原作者過去亦曾發表右翼言論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JgXeblfVZv3gllNOoPToNHl670E=/802x325/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OZSN6MUSBFA5LGOUCAZ7OYC4PY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJgXeblfVZv3gllNOoPToNHl670E%3D%2F802x325%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOZSN6MUSBFA5LGOUCAZ7OYC4PY.jpg&h=e429242f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而事實上，《鬼滅》受到各方批評後，電影於下月在韓國上畫前，已經將炭治郎的耳環設計更改，將旗上太陽的光線，改為在太陽之下。不過你有你鬧，《鬼滅》韓國版漫畫及畫集在當地的銷量依然強勁，畫集初版發行未夠一個月已經全部沽清。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7zoV4ORPq2994CVeZzhND1mN38I=/802x1142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YVVALXHZJZEEBP7UQA7IVJXLMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7zoV4ORPq2994CVeZzhND1mN38I%3D%2F802x1142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYVVALXHZJZEEBP7UQA7IVJXLMI.jpg&h=4b753b73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48dd3a960992f6f8d7aced8562e32e6ada1ab33e","tid":2286279,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T01:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a3b4bc7a8deaa6b64a533035dc23dc0dd1d291","tid":2286279,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4394fe0bf454c2326814ba10ad314c2bbcfba8","tid":2286279,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"好撚心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔合作遲早比人食埋兩個"},{"pid":"8f52618be1de3125fa14496bc7a2bc0e0efe3751","tid":2286279,"uid":58076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:48:15.000Z","msg":"驚咪唔好上映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f25fe944cde79f63e559ee2389e2472d8ef57df","tid":2286279,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:49:59.000Z","msg":"原來鬼滅係咁右的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d9d2a331d1ffe5ce05e012f36435797a62b092","tid":2286279,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:53:56.000Z","msg":"反而好奇點解玻璃心國人冇出黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5095c73256955df6b537d7f83d23d56cf867436","tid":2286279,"uid":144773,"